═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
[SECTION 1] OVERVIEW - WHAT IS THE TWO-PANEL SYSTEM?
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

The Simpler Trading dashboard uses a TWO-PANEL SIDEBAR SYSTEM where:

┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                                                                       │
│  [PANEL 1]              [MAIN CONTENT]              [PANEL 2]       │
│  Primary Sidebar        Dashboard Area              Content Sidebar  │
│  (Always visible)       (Changes based on page)     (Conditional)   │
│                                                                       │
│  280px wide             Flexible width               260px wide      │
│  Blue #0f2d41           White/Gray #f4f4f4          White #fff      │
│                                                                       │
│  Shows:                 Shows:                       Shows:          │
│  - Profile              - Page title                 - Sub-menu      │
│  - Main nav             - Membership cards           - Context nav   │
│  - Categories           - Tools                      - Quick links   │
│  - All memberships      - Content                    - Resources     │
│                                                                       │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

KEY CONCEPT:
Panel 1 (Primary) = ALWAYS VISIBLE on all dashboard pages
Panel 2 (Secondary) = ONLY VISIBLE on individual membership pages

═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
[SECTION 2] PANEL 1 - PRIMARY SIDEBAR (BLUE PANEL)
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

LOCATION IN JESUS FILE: Line 3059
HTML ELEMENT: <aside class="dashboard__sidebar">
CSS CLASS: .dashboard__sidebar
BACKGROUND COLOR: #0f2d41 (Dark blue)
WIDTH: 280px
POSITION: Fixed on left side of screen

─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
WHAT IT CONTAINS:
─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

[2.1] PROFILE SECTION (Top of sidebar)
├─ User's profile photo (circular, 34px × 34px)
├─ User's name (white text, 16px, weight 400)
└─ Links to: /dashboard/account

[2.2] MAIN NAVIGATION LINKS
├─ Member Dashboard → /dashboard (home icon)
├─ My Classes → /dashboard/classes (courses icon)
└─ My Indicators → /dashboard/indicators (indicators icon)

[2.3] MEMBERSHIPS CATEGORY
├─ Header: "MEMBERSHIPS" (uppercase, 10px, weight 700)
└─ Lists all trading rooms user has access to:
    ├─ Mastering the Trade
    ├─ Simpler Showcase
    ├─ Options Trading
    ├─ Day Trading
    └─ (etc. - dynamically populated based on user's subscriptions)

[2.4] MASTERY CATEGORY
├─ Header: "MASTERY" (uppercase, 10px, weight 700)
└─ Lists all courses user owns:
    ├─ Options 101
    ├─ Chart Patterns
    ├─ Fibonacci Trading
    └─ (etc. - dynamically populated)

[2.5] PREMIUM REPORTS CATEGORY
├─ Header: "PREMIUM REPORTS" (uppercase, 10px, weight 700)
└─ Lists premium content:
    └─ Weekly Watchlist

[2.6] TOOLS CATEGORY
├─ Header: "TOOLS" (uppercase, 10px, weight 700)
└─ Links to:
    ├─ Weekly Watchlist → /dashboard/ww
    └─ Support → https://intercom.help/simpler-trading/en/

[2.7] ACCOUNT CATEGORY
├─ Header: "ACCOUNT" (uppercase, 10px, weight 700)
└─ Links to:
    └─ My Account → /dashboard/account

