─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
WHEN IS PANEL 1 VISIBLE?
─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

ALWAYS VISIBLE on:
✓ Main dashboard landing page (/dashboard)
✓ Individual membership pages (/dashboard/mastering-the-trade)
✓ Course pages (/dashboard/classes)
✓ Account settings (/dashboard/account)
✓ ALL dashboard pages

RESPONSIVE BEHAVIOR:
├─ Desktop (1280px+): Always visible, 280px wide
├─ Tablet/Mobile (<1280px): Hidden by default, slides in from left when menu button clicked
└─ Mobile menu button: Fixed at bottom of screen, 50px tall, #0d2532 background

